This paper deals with the problem of facial attribute transfer, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of deep learning techniques, which are often used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method also involves the use of facial landmarks, which are a form of geometric information (cs.GR). Finally, the paper discusses the generation of high-resolution images, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
